timeline.bodyText:
I'm not sure why you are using reflection here. As far as I can tell, you can simply do this:
ArrangedWriter arrangedXmlWriter = new ArrangedWriter(rdfXmlWriter);

But to be honest, I think you can get rid of using the ArrangedWriter as part of this test completely, as it's not really necessary for testing that the COMPACT_XML setting works.

